To remove redundant CUDA kernels, I changed the schedule impl in cuda.reduction by adding a specific "EnableAutoInline" condition for auto-inlining the injective operations. But I don't know if there is a better way to solve this problem. Welcome for more suggestions and discussion.

 * Otherwise, stale pytest-results could appear in builds.
 * See #8593 

